WEBVTT

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.292
Big sister, wait for me.

00:00:15.958 --> 00:00:17.417
Big sister!

00:00:19.083 --> 00:00:20.500
What the hell is going on?

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.042
AFTER THE INVASION, BEFORE FORMER DEPARTMENT OF RESEARCH & DEVELOPMENT
Why are you drawing out here?

00:00:23.042 --> 00:00:26.292
Shouldn't you be inside getting ready?

00:00:26.292 --> 00:00:31.667
What? While I was waiting for you guys,
didn't I finish preparation?

00:00:32.958 --> 00:00:35.333
Where's the cat granny?

00:00:35.333 --> 00:00:37.667
Miss Yoruichi has gone up first.

00:00:37.667 --> 00:00:39.542
Haha, I'm going to tattle.

00:00:39.542 --> 00:00:41.125
That idiot. As soon as
I mentioned cat granny,

00:00:41.125 --> 00:00:43.167
- I got an immediate answer.
- Okay, let's go in anyway.

00:00:43.167 --> 00:00:44.958
Wait a minute.

00:00:44.958 --> 00:00:46.917
Why did you let them go first?

00:00:46.917 --> 00:00:51.417
Didn't we agree to
go together after we met?

00:00:52.208 --> 00:00:54.625
Because the situation changed.

00:00:54.625 --> 00:00:56.458
So what if it changed?

00:00:56.458 --> 00:01:00.042
What if they die?

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:05.292
Do you believe buying time from the enemy
is more important than keeping them alive?

00:01:05.292 --> 00:01:09.042
That's why you sent
Ichigo and Yoruichi off, right?

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:12.542
What?

00:01:12.542 --> 00:01:16.583
Is big sister already gone?

00:01:16.583 --> 00:01:18.333
No way.

00:01:18.333 --> 00:01:21.333
It was unusual for her to call me.

00:01:21.333 --> 00:01:27.125
I brought so many things
here to help her out.

00:01:27.125 --> 00:01:28.917
I'm sorry.

00:01:28.917 --> 00:01:33.917
It's all for the sake of Seireitei
that I sent Miss Yoruichi there first.

00:01:33.917 --> 00:01:35.875
Please forgive me.

00:01:35.875 --> 00:01:37.958
23RD HEAD OF THE SHIHOIN CLAN,
YUSHIRO SHIHOIN

00:01:37.958 --> 00:01:39.792
Alright then.

00:01:39.792 --> 00:01:44.208
The things you brought will
definitely be able to help your sister.

00:01:44.208 --> 00:01:46.208
Please come in.

00:01:46.208 --> 00:01:47.958
I recall now.

00:01:47.958 --> 00:01:54.958
I can't stand whenever you say,
"for the sake of Seireitei."

00:03:22.958 --> 00:03:26.000
(BLEACH: Thousand-Year Blood War)

00:03:27.042 --> 00:03:31.833
May I pass, Ichibe Hyosube?

00:03:33.417 --> 00:03:38.292
Despite my repeated warnings,
you still call me by name.

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:42.833
Don't blame me
if your throat gets crushed.

00:03:45.417 --> 00:03:48.792
Your king is so bad
that he fled on his own.

00:03:48.792 --> 00:03:52.208
Then I'll have no choice
but to kill his heir.

00:03:52.208 --> 00:03:55.375
Who is his heir?

00:03:58.708 --> 00:04:01.083
From here.

00:04:04.125 --> 00:04:06.500
To here.

00:04:06.500 --> 00:04:09.458
I will defeat you within this range.

00:04:10.083 --> 00:04:12.417
It appears to be a fairly broad range.

00:04:12.417 --> 00:04:18.042
I only have three more steps
to take before you die, Ichibe Hyosube.

00:04:23.833 --> 00:04:25.875
I've told you.

00:04:25.875 --> 00:04:29.375
Don't casually call me by name.

00:04:35.958 --> 00:04:38.375
Senri Tsutensho.

00:04:38.375 --> 00:04:43.625
Whatever this hand strikes will
fly thousands of miles away.

00:04:44.500 --> 00:04:48.167
Didn't I tell you?

00:04:48.167 --> 00:04:51.792
Don't blame me
if your throat gets crushed.

00:04:54.083 --> 00:04:56.667
Just keep going for
another thousand miles.

00:04:56.667 --> 00:04:59.083
Do some serious introspection.

00:05:06.792 --> 00:05:10.167
I give voice to myself.

00:05:10.167 --> 00:05:12.792
Sankt Bogen!

00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:31.208
I didn't expect you to rocket yourself
upward by shooting yourself.

00:05:31.208 --> 00:05:33.125
You're so annoying.

00:05:33.125 --> 00:05:39.417
You called me by name after I asked
you not to. You came back after I hit you.

00:05:39.417 --> 00:05:45.458
Despite your age,
you're still a mischievous brat.

00:05:45.458 --> 00:05:49.958
I have no choice
since you won't listen to me.

00:05:50.958 --> 00:05:53.000
I can only kill you.

00:05:56.500 --> 00:06:00.250
I'll wait for you to be mentally prepared.

00:06:00.250 --> 00:06:04.042
But it makes no difference
to me who I kill first.

00:06:08.458 --> 00:06:14.125
Regret it. You shouldn't be grateful
you don't fight His Majesty.

00:06:31.917 --> 00:06:34.875
Whatever power you used,

00:06:34.875 --> 00:06:38.792
it wasn't enough to break my confinement.

00:06:48.125 --> 00:06:50.000
I'm in, too.

00:06:50.792 --> 00:06:52.500
Take this!

00:06:59.333 --> 00:07:01.125
What a waste to end the bath so quickly

00:07:01.125 --> 00:07:04.208
in such a lovely hot spring.

00:07:10.833 --> 00:07:14.958
After I vanquish you, I'll consider
whether or not to bathe in it.

00:07:15.750 --> 00:07:19.000
I'll show you what outdoor
hot spring sunbathing is like.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.667
Kinpika.

00:07:27.250 --> 00:07:33.125
I finally got to show off my skills,
but others took my prey.

00:07:33.125 --> 00:07:35.917
And Yuha is there too.

00:07:38.833 --> 00:07:41.500
It's not over yet.

00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:46.750
That is insufficient to kill me.

00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:48.875
What?

00:07:48.875 --> 00:07:51.583
His Majesty only took me in

00:07:51.583 --> 00:07:55.167
because I couldn't die.

00:07:55.167 --> 00:07:57.833
Is my ability that useless?

00:07:57.833 --> 00:07:59.542
I hate it the most.

00:07:59.542 --> 00:08:06.667
When I think of my power,
I feel as if I'm on the verge of death.

00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:10.292
My Schrift is D.

00:08:10.292 --> 00:08:13.333
My power is The Deathdealing.

00:08:13.333 --> 00:08:17.417
I can calculate the perfect lethal dose
of any substance

00:08:17.417 --> 00:08:20.458
I take into my body that cause death.

00:08:20.458 --> 00:08:24.208
I can even change the amount as I see fit.

00:08:24.208 --> 00:08:26.083
What?

00:08:26.083 --> 00:08:28.792
It's difficult to understand, right?

00:08:28.792 --> 00:08:31.208
I didn't get it at first either.

00:08:31.208 --> 00:08:35.500
But you don't need to know.
Even if you don't understand, it's okay.

00:08:35.500 --> 00:08:39.458
All you need to know is
that you're going to die.

00:08:42.208 --> 00:08:47.958
I'm lowering the lethal dose
of blood in your body.

00:08:49.042 --> 00:08:54.875
When the blood that allows you
to sustain life flows more in your body,

00:08:54.875 --> 00:08:57.958
you are getting closer to death.

00:08:57.958 --> 00:09:01.083
You must be in pain.
There's nothing you can do about it.

00:09:01.083 --> 00:09:03.750
This is what it feels like to be lethal.

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:05.667
I understand it very well.

00:09:09.417 --> 00:09:11.958
Because we are the same.

00:09:15.750 --> 00:09:21.500
I won't let you take and collect
the Reishi of confinement.

00:09:27.583 --> 00:09:29.333
Licht Regen.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:42.208
That is too weak.

00:09:42.208 --> 00:09:44.750
it's just like a spring rain.

00:09:45.667 --> 00:09:47.917
What's wrong?

00:09:47.917 --> 00:09:50.583
I am about to break
the shield you are so proud of.

00:09:51.958 --> 00:09:54.250
Do you think you can break it?

00:09:54.250 --> 00:09:56.500
Of course. Isn't it obvious?

00:09:58.125 --> 00:10:00.292
You blocked it?

00:10:00.292 --> 00:10:02.125
Impossible.

00:10:18.583 --> 00:10:20.667
You're almost dying, aren't you?

00:10:20.667 --> 00:10:22.958
You've never taken me seriously, have you?

00:10:22.958 --> 00:10:25.375
In either my manner of speech
or the impressions I give,

00:10:25.375 --> 00:10:28.375
I must appear to you as a nobody.

00:10:28.375 --> 00:10:32.000
But it doesn't matter.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:35.000
Although I used to care a lot.

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:41.667
Lately I keep telling myself
that this is my strength.

00:10:41.667 --> 00:10:47.375
Being gloomy can give other a fatal blow.

00:10:47.375 --> 00:10:50.375
Thanks for your explanation.

00:10:58.500 --> 00:11:05.875
Since you lowered my blood's lethal dose,
too much blood will kill me.

00:11:05.875 --> 00:11:12.083
Then all I have to do is let the blood out
till it is below the lethal dose.

00:11:12.083 --> 00:11:14.500
You're so reckless.

00:11:14.500 --> 00:11:18.083
But it's not that simple.

00:11:18.083 --> 00:11:22.792
You should weigh roughly 60 kg.

00:11:22.792 --> 00:11:28.250
You make an accurate guess
just like a doctor. I weigh 62 kg.

00:11:28.250 --> 00:11:34.292
The amount of blood per kg
is approximately 65.7 milliliters.

00:11:34.292 --> 00:11:37.417
If you weigh 62 kg,
it is approximately 4 liters.

00:11:37.417 --> 00:11:42.000
If you lose 2 liters, half of your blood,
you would die from blood loss.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:45.083
Your current lethal dose of blood

00:11:45.083 --> 00:11:47.833
is roughly 1.6 liters.

00:11:47.833 --> 00:11:51.667
That is, even if you don't drain
all of your blood until you die,

00:11:51.667 --> 00:11:55.125
you will be killed by
your own blood in the end.

00:11:55.125 --> 00:12:01.667
It's likely that you no longer know
whether you're standing or laying down.

00:12:01.667 --> 00:12:04.750
I see. That's a headache.

00:12:04.750 --> 00:12:07.708
What am I supposed to do,

00:12:07.708 --> 00:12:10.625
Tenjiro?

00:12:13.250 --> 00:12:14.750
Are you surprised?

00:12:14.750 --> 00:12:19.417
Tenjiro's hot spring has the ability
to extract blood and Spiritual Pressure.

00:12:19.417 --> 00:12:22.667
But that refers to the white hot spring.

00:12:22.667 --> 00:12:28.542
And for this red hot spring, it can
replenish all lost blood with new blood.

00:12:35.375 --> 00:12:40.000
Do I look cool after the rebirth?

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:43.333
Yes, you look cool.

00:12:43.333 --> 00:12:46.125
Compared with you, I am...

00:12:46.125 --> 00:12:49.042
I thought I won in the end.

00:12:49.042 --> 00:12:52.333
I underestimated you.

00:12:53.458 --> 00:12:55.917
That's killing me.

00:13:02.250 --> 00:13:05.583
I don't mind rain,

00:13:05.583 --> 00:13:09.167
but I despise getting my clothes wet.

00:13:24.042 --> 00:13:28.000
So this is the battle of the Squad 0.

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:32.375
Well, monk, it's all up
to your performance now.

00:13:35.042 --> 00:13:38.792
Your expression has changed dramatically.

00:13:38.792 --> 00:13:40.583
Is that so?

00:13:40.583 --> 00:13:42.917
You seem really happy.

00:13:42.917 --> 00:13:48.667
But you have taken on a ferocious
expression when you determined to kill me.

00:13:53.708 --> 00:13:57.042
However, is that all you got
even after your expression has changed?

00:13:57.042 --> 00:13:59.875
You blocked it with your arm?

00:13:59.875 --> 00:14:03.458
My brush can't cut flesh,

00:14:03.458 --> 00:14:06.125
and it can cut names.

00:14:07.375 --> 00:14:12.292
I just cut your arm's name in half.

00:14:12.292 --> 00:14:15.667
Now, you have only the half of the name.

00:14:15.667 --> 00:14:18.292
Does your arm feel very heavy?

00:14:18.292 --> 00:14:21.750
Only half of your muscle strength
and half of your abilities remain.

00:14:21.750 --> 00:14:26.750
Your arm can now only do half
of what it once could.

00:14:28.833 --> 00:14:33.333
You'll be too weak
to even wield your sword.

00:14:33.333 --> 00:14:37.208
Look, you're cut in half.

00:14:47.917 --> 00:14:52.667
What do you think after being cut in half?

00:14:52.667 --> 00:14:57.667
How does it feel to be defeated by

00:14:57.667 --> 00:15:01.083
Soul Reaper leader you loathe
who uses half strength,

00:15:01.083 --> 00:15:06.917
the leader of Quincies
with half of the abilities?

00:15:06.917 --> 00:15:09.375
VISORED

00:15:09.375 --> 00:15:11.958
CONFINEMENT

00:15:23.583 --> 00:15:25.250
Wait a moment.

00:15:26.083 --> 00:15:29.250
Don't suck so much blood at one go.

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:32.542
I don't want to die yet.

00:15:32.542 --> 00:15:35.583
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:15:36.333 --> 00:15:46.625
How many times do I have to tell you
that you're already dead?

00:15:46.625 --> 00:15:52.792
Give me back my blood!

00:16:03.292 --> 00:16:05.542
Bambi, you're so cute.

00:16:05.542 --> 00:16:08.917
So cute. You're even cute when dead.

00:16:08.917 --> 00:16:10.625
I like you. I really do.

00:16:10.625 --> 00:16:12.542
Like you.

00:16:15.250 --> 00:16:19.625
Got you. So you're still alive.

00:16:20.375 --> 00:16:22.625
Of course.

00:16:22.625 --> 00:16:24.417
What happened to your face?

00:16:24.417 --> 00:16:26.125
It appears that
you have been severely beaten.

00:16:26.125 --> 00:16:28.750
Did you lose?

00:16:28.750 --> 00:16:30.625
I was beaten by PePe.

00:16:30.625 --> 00:16:31.917
Lousy.

00:16:31.917 --> 00:16:33.125
Shut up.

00:16:33.125 --> 00:16:34.542
What happened to PePe?

00:16:34.542 --> 00:16:37.042
I killed him. He's not very tasty.

00:16:37.042 --> 00:16:39.000
That's gross.

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:41.083
Where are Minnie and Candy?

00:16:41.083 --> 00:16:42.750
Candy went to deal with the enemy.

00:16:42.750 --> 00:16:46.042
Minnie was mind-controlled
by PePe and I knocked her out.

00:16:46.042 --> 00:16:47.792
She should be still alive.

00:16:47.792 --> 00:16:52.208
We can't waste our power
before His Majesty arrives.

00:16:52.208 --> 00:16:54.750
Will he really come down?

00:16:56.583 --> 00:17:03.083
Yuha, it appears like a thousand years
is too short for you to reflect.

00:17:03.083 --> 00:17:07.917
But don't worry.
I won't keep you reflecting long.

00:17:07.917 --> 00:17:11.583
You just have to reflect until eternity.

00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:25.167
Rise, the badge of silver, grey plains,
and the ring road hidden by the aura.

00:17:25.167 --> 00:17:28.458
The onyx eyeball, the golden tongue.

00:17:28.458 --> 00:17:33.000
The cup of the skull,
the coffin of the gods.

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:37.000
The thing you hold high is your heart.

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:48.000
What's wrong?

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:51.208
Auswahlen.

00:17:58.167 --> 00:18:00.625
What's that light?

00:18:02.500 --> 00:18:05.375
I don't feel good. Let's run.

00:18:10.917 --> 00:18:12.875
Damn it, my wings...

00:18:12.875 --> 00:18:15.750
Are our powers waning?

00:18:15.750 --> 00:18:17.250
What's going on?

00:18:20.792 --> 00:18:22.167
Reishi...

00:18:22.167 --> 00:18:23.125
No.

00:18:23.125 --> 00:18:27.750
Even the power inscribed within
souls has been taken away?

00:18:34.417 --> 00:18:36.292
What's happening?

00:18:36.292 --> 00:18:38.667
What's happening, Your Majesty?

00:18:38.667 --> 00:18:41.458
What the hell is going on?

00:18:41.458 --> 00:18:45.250
What on earth are we to you?

00:18:45.250 --> 00:18:47.250
Of course, you're my companions.

00:18:49.500 --> 00:18:52.208
What's wrong? What's happened?

00:18:52.208 --> 00:18:54.917
I was about to ask the same thing.

00:18:54.917 --> 00:18:59.625
Your Majesty, is this your doing?

00:19:01.958 --> 00:19:04.208
Bambi, I'm not going to die.

00:19:04.208 --> 00:19:06.667
I'm not going to die, Bambi.

00:19:06.667 --> 00:19:07.833
I definitely won't die.

00:19:07.833 --> 00:19:09.667
Of course.

00:19:09.667 --> 00:19:11.583
Who's going to die?

00:19:11.583 --> 00:19:13.292
How could I...

00:19:13.292 --> 00:19:16.625
How could I die here?

00:19:17.500 --> 00:19:20.583
Nanao, Okikiba.

00:19:20.583 --> 00:19:23.125
May I leave the Squad 1?

00:19:24.542 --> 00:19:27.458
The Soul King Palace is in peril,

00:19:27.458 --> 00:19:30.333
not Seireitei.

00:19:43.125 --> 00:19:45.292
What's going on?

00:20:08.708 --> 00:20:13.625
You definitely are ruthless, stealing
the abilities of your companions.

00:20:14.958 --> 00:20:19.417
We are companions, and we help each other.

00:20:19.417 --> 00:20:21.625
Resurrect.

00:20:21.625 --> 00:20:24.667
Keep going.

00:20:24.667 --> 00:20:26.583
What's this situation?

00:20:26.583 --> 00:20:28.542
Auswahlen.

00:20:28.542 --> 00:20:31.958
Take the life and power
of unnecessary Quincies

00:20:31.958 --> 00:20:36.417
and transfer them to those in need.
This is power reallocation.

00:20:36.417 --> 00:20:38.625
Those who lose their power die.

00:20:38.625 --> 00:20:42.792
Those who gain power not only
get stronger, but they can also revive.

00:20:42.792 --> 00:20:46.042
It's one of His Majesty's abilities.

00:20:46.042 --> 00:20:48.458
The scale has been tipped.

00:20:48.458 --> 00:20:49.708
(BLEACH Episode 25)

00:20:50.333 --> 00:20:53.708
We will obliterate Squad 0.

00:20:53.708 --> 00:20:56.000
(The Master)

00:22:29.292 --> 00:22:34.083
Oh my, everything
is completely destroyed.

00:22:35.208 --> 00:22:43.625
Can we rebuild the Seireitei's structures
after defeating the enemy?

00:22:43.625 --> 00:22:46.875
What do you think, Ukitake?

00:22:48.042 --> 00:22:53.292
It makes no difference whether it can be
restored or destroyed. Simply rebuild it.

00:22:53.292 --> 00:22:55.542
I knew you would say that.

00:22:55.542 --> 00:22:58.750
They were the ones who allowed the enemy
to invade Soul King Palace, right?

00:22:58.750 --> 00:23:01.000
You've noticed?

00:23:01.000 --> 00:23:03.875
Kamikake has already foreseen this.

00:23:05.708 --> 00:23:07.583
Yeah.

00:23:07.583 --> 00:23:10.583
It seems Kamikake was successful.

00:23:13.083 --> 00:23:16.583
So, it wouldn't be a problem
if you showed off a bit, right?

00:23:16.583 --> 00:23:19.167
You sound like a doctor.

00:23:20.333 --> 00:23:22.750
I'm leaving. Be careful on your own.

00:23:22.750 --> 00:23:24.125
See you later.

00:23:24.583 --> 00:23:28.333
Wait. Where are you going, Kyoraku?

00:23:28.333 --> 00:23:32.292
I'm going for a drink.

00:23:35.542 --> 00:23:39.292
Catch the lines falling from the clouds.

00:23:39.292 --> 00:23:41.417
Splash, splash.

00:23:41.417 --> 00:23:46.458
Falling onto the white fields
and becoming skeletons.

00:23:46.458 --> 00:23:48.750
(BLEACH Episode 26: Black)

